<!-- The uptime tile's hero stat: a markup SPAN PARAGRAPH — the bold value
     run inside one heading-size paragraph — compiled at comptime
     (canvas.CompiledMarkupView) like the spark fragments and placed as an
     ordinary child of the Zig tile. The 239 width is the tile plot
     geometry (view.zig's spark_width constant); the label mirrors the
     visible value so assistive tech announces the stat by name. -->
<text size="heading" width="239" label="{uptimeValue}"><span weight="bold">{uptimeValue}</span></text>
